{"tid":1918373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"光復高雄發言人：相約大家脫下口罩，在沒有韓國瑜的高雄相見","createTime":"2020-03-10T05:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T11:44:19.000Z","uid":52658,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7c0552ed1a93e067bf0ed69229d86707fc3487","tid":1918373,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"〔記者王榮祥／高雄報導〕百日罷韓、光復高雄！40萬份包裹在遮羞布下的罷韓連署書，今上午由罷韓團體正式送交高市選委會；罷韓領銜人陳冠榮醫師指出，今天是罷韓二階連署終點，也是罷韓最終目標的起點，他跟大家相約一百天後，在沒有韓國瑜的高雄見。<br />\n<br />\nWecare高雄、公民割草行動、台灣基進等罷韓團體今上午先透過車隊，將40萬分罷韓連署書載運到鳳山行政中心前與志工群會合後，再以步行遊行方式前往高市選委會，沿途不斷高呼百日罷韓、光復高雄，遊行隊伍氣氛熱烈，頗有1221大遊行的味道。<br />\n<br />\n#光復高雄<br />\n#保衛台灣"},{"pid":"2a627b15f28608e8924d7f9b7a0a237299b3fe6a","tid":1918373,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea384ce2e5cd25a9ae0aa285e84d46a50261c04","tid":1918373,"uid":103230,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:09:17.000Z","msg":"公民割草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b25af4f0883de48250a8bff65827160f9b07d63","tid":1918373,"uid":52658,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGxaukQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGxaukQ.jpg&h=0599fbbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7eb14ba99f072c2c0f932230baf74ee776e3565","tid":1918373,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h